high_descs: Turn around to your left walk straight then turn left move slightly then turn left facing the island
Pick up the knife beside the apple on the island
Turn to your right then walk straight then turn left head to the sink
Put the knife in the sink and rinse it
Turn around to your left then face the drawer below the toaster
Open the drawer and put inside the knife then close it again
anns.task_desc: Put the clean knife in the drawer.

high_descs: Turn around, proceed around rounded counter.  Stop in front of knife with apple behind it.
Pick up knife from directly in front of apple.
Put knife in sink left of spoon and green sponge.  Fill sink and empty it.  Pick up same knife.
Turn left three times and proceed to counter to the right of the stove.
Open top drawer, place knife on the right hand side and close drawer.
anns.task_desc: Move knife from counter, clean it and put it in a drawer.

high_descs: Walk to the left side of the table.
Grab the knife in front of you.
Turn the faucet on, and soak the knife.
Go to the kitchen drawer and open it.
Place the knife in the drawer and close it.
anns.task_desc: Get a knife from the table to soak it and put it in the drawer.
